---
import SocialList from "@/components/SocialList.astro";
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "About Shawn Lin and this site.",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-8">About</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none" lang="en">
		<p>
			I am a full-stack engineer currently focused on full-stack development,
			security, AI-assisted development, and agentic workflows.
		</p>
		<p>
			I like exploring new tools and development practices, then bringing them
			into real workflows. For me, the tool itself is not the point. What
			matters is whether it helps us validate ideas faster, reduce repetitive
			work, or make a vague problem easier to reason about.
		</p>
		<p>
			AI tools have changed quickly over the past few years, and I have spent a
			lot of time exploring how they can participate in development and testing:
			from breaking down requirements, writing code, debugging, and organizing
			documentation, to building agentic workflows that support security testing
			and product iteration.
		</p>
		<p>
			This site is my public notebook. I write about engineering work, tool
			experiments, debugging stories, deployment notes, and thoughts from
			adjusting how I work. It is not exactly a portfolio, and not exactly a
			collection of polished essays. It is closer to a workbench that keeps
			getting reorganized.
		</p>
		<p>
			I enjoy exchanging ideas with people. If you are interested in
			AI-assisted development, agentic systems, security testing, developer
			tools, or personal knowledge management, feel free to
			<a class="cactus-link" href="mailto:shawndennislin@gmail.com">email me</a>.
		</p>
	</div>

	<hr class="my-10 border-border" />

	<div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none" lang="zh-Hant">
		<p>
			我是一名全端工程師，最近關注的主題主要在全端開發、資安、AI-assisted
			development，以及 Agentic workflow。
		</p>
		<p>
			我喜歡研究新的工具和開發方式，然後把它們放進實際工作流裡。對我來說，工具本身不是重點，重點是它能不能幫助我們更快驗證想法、減少重複工作，或讓一個模糊的問題變得比較清楚。
		</p>
		<p>
			這幾年 AI
			工具變化很快，我花了很多時間探索它們可以怎麼參與開發與測試：從需求拆解、寫程式、除錯、整理文件，到建立一些能輔助資安測試與產品迭代的
			Agentic workflow。
		</p>
		<p>
			這個網站是我的公開筆記，會記錄工程實作、工具實驗、踩坑過程、部署經驗，以及我在調整工作方式時留下的想法。它不完全是作品集，也不完全是正式文章集，比較像是一個持續整理中的工作台。
		</p>
		<p>
			我也很喜歡和人交流想法。如果你對 AI-assisted development、Agentic
			systems、資安測試、開發者工具，或個人知識管理有興趣，歡迎<a
				class="cactus-link"
				href="mailto:shawndennislin@gmail.com">寄信給我</a
			>。
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="mt-10">
		<SocialList />
	</div>
</PageLayout>
